text: Erik Styf (4 December 1932 - 1 April 2001) was a Swedish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:2001 deaths Category:Swedish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Sweden Category:Ski jumpers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:People from Sundsvall
